manifest.name: Image Upload Toolkit
manifest.description: An obsidian plugin for uploading local images embedded in markdown to remote store and export markdown for publishing to static site. Currently, it supports Imgur and Aliyun OSS.
manifest.author: Addo Zhang

data.manifestValue: An obsidian plugin for uploading local images embedded in markdown to remote store and export markdown for publishing to static site. Currently, it supports Imgur and Aliyun OSS.
data.communityListValue: Upload local images embedded in Markdown to remote store and export Markdown with image public URL for publishing to static site. Currently, it supports Imgur, Aliyun OSS, ImageKit and AWS S3.
